Rancor:

     He decided against going to the decpticon base, and turned to the coast. As he stood on the beach he looked out and saw the other continent. He knew that he could swim, fairly well too. He transformed back to beast mode and jumped in the water.

     "Swimming!" He thought to himself. "Swimming it fun! Swimming is...not something I can do in beast mode!!!" He started to sink, then realized that he didn't need oxygen, "Oh, yeah...I'm a robot!"

     He began to walk across the ocean in between the continents, soon to reach the other side...
